go where I know the tunnels are.

537
00:32:00,447 --> 00:32:01,760
Right.

538
00:32:01,859 --> 00:32:04,127
Excuse me.

539
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:10,760
Wait a minute.

540
00:32:15,970 --> 00:32:18,270
Come with me.

541
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:24,558
