598
00:35:27,867 --> 00:35:30,590
Don't you, melinda?

599
00:35:33,860 --> 00:35:36,590
Dad?

600
00:35:41,730 --> 00:35:45,563
Ok, if this is city hall,
and that's the old theater,

601
00:35:45,662 --> 00:35:50,550
then the closest building to the
alley that fed into church street is...

602
00:35:51,380 --> 00:35:52,603
right there.

603
00:35:52,702 --> 00:35:54,103
What a coincidence.

604
00:35:54,202 --> 00:35:57,618
I don't know about you, but I'm beginning
to think that there's no such thing.

605
00:35:57,717 --> 00:35:59,673
How did find me?

606
00:35:59,772 --> 00:36:01,188
Where have you been? Did you die?

607
00:36:01,287 --> 00:36:02,613
