myself walk into this.

611
00:36:10,547 --> 00:36:12,108
I... everybody told
me to stay away.

612
00:36:12,207 --> 00:36:13,958
You didn't walk into anything.

613
00:36:14,057 --> 00:36:15,650
You were led here.

614
00:36:15,749 --> 00:36:17,308
