your gift, not hide it.

636
00:37:12,547 --> 00:37:13,663
I don't understand.

637
00:37:13,762 --> 00:37:16,558
The locket is not from my side of
the family. It's from your mother'S.

638
00:37:16,657 --> 00:37:19,010
She wanted to bury
that part of your past,

639
00:37:19,109 --> 00:37:21,428
